cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with computer vision and robotics, specifically with pose estimation of a human hand using point clouds provided by the Kinect sensor. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.RO (Robotics) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also deals with the classification of different types of interactions, which falls under the sub-category of cs.GR (Graphics). The use of the Iterative Closest Point (ICP) algorithm for pose estimation falls under the sub-categories of cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
